<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="86" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1436,152,940]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,309,498,521]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">Remarks.</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation box="[315,458,498,521]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref1039" refString="Evans, W. H. (1949) A catalogue of the Hesperiidae from Europe, Asia &amp; Australia in the British Museum (Natural History). The British Museum, London, 502 pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 105941" type="book">Evans (1949)</bibRefCitation>
recorded one male 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1882" box="[667,819,497,521]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Halpe" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sikkima">
<emphasis box="[667,819,497,521]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">Halpe sikkima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingRegion box="[884,964,498,521]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">Hainan</collectingRegion>
. Since then, no more material of this species has been collected from this place again, although field surveys have been carried out on the island repeatedly, and a number of hesperiid species have been published as new to science (
<bibRefCitation box="[884,1007,568,591]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref887" refString="Chou, I. (Ed.) (1994) Monographia Rhopalocerorum Sinensium. Henan Scientific and Technological Publishing House, Zhengzhou, 854 pp." type="book">Chou 1994</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation box="[1019,1196,567,591]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref1139" refString="Fan, X. L., Wang, M. &amp; Zeng, L. (2007 a) The genus Idmon de Niceville (Lepidoptera: Hesperiidae) from China, withdescription of two new species. Zootaxa, 1510, 57 - 62." type="journal article">
Fan 
<emphasis box="[1066,1113,567,591]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">et al</emphasis>
. 2007a
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation box="[1207,1385,567,591]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref1186" refString="Fan, X. L., Wang, M., Chen, L. S. &amp; Zeng, L. (2007 b) The genus Zographetus Watson (Lepidoptera: Hesperiidae) in China, with the description of two new species. Entomological News, 118 (3), 296 - 302." type="journal article">
Fan 
<emphasis box="[1254,1300,567,591]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">et al</emphasis>
. 2007b
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref1091" refString="Fan, X. L. &amp; Chiba, H. (2008) A new species of the genus Hyarotis Moore (Lepidoptera: Hesperiidae) from China. Journal of South China Agricultural University, 29 (2), 74 - 75, 85." type="journal article">Fan &amp; Chiba 2008</bibRefCitation>
) or discovered as new records to the skipper fauna of 
<collectingCountry box="[898,962,602,625]" name="China" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">China</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation box="[977,1146,601,625]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref1245" refString="Fan, X. L., Huang, G. H., Wang, M., Wang, C. D. &amp; Su, W. B. (2003) A newly recorded genus and species of the skippers from China (Lepidoptera: Hesperiidae). Journal of South China Agricultural University, Natural Science Edition, 24 (4), 56 - 57." type="journal article">
Fan 
<emphasis box="[1027,1074,601,625]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">et al</emphasis>
. 2003
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation box="[1158,1321,601,625]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref1317" refString="Fei, W., Huang, Z. F., Chiba, H. &amp; Fan, X. L. (2015) Capila lidderdali (Elwes, 1888), a newly recorded skipper from China (Lepidoptera: Hesperiidae). Journal of Environmental Entomology, 37 (1), 184 - 186." type="journal article">
Fei 
<emphasis box="[1201,1248,601,625]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">et al</emphasis>
. 2015
</bibRefCitation>
). In recent literature specializing in the fauna of 
<collectingRegion box="[547,624,637,660]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">Hainan</collectingRegion>
skippers (e.g. 
<bibRefCitation box="[779,964,637,660]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref1418" refString="Gu, M. B. &amp; Chen, P. Z. (1997) Butterflies in Hainan Island. China Forestry Publishing House, Beijing, 355 pp." type="book">Gu &amp; Chen 1997</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation box="[974,1069,637,660]" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" refId="ref1377" refString="Gu, M. B. (2002) Lepidoptera: Rhopalocera. In: Huang F. S. (Ed.), Forest Insects of Hainan. Science Press, Beijing, pp. 654 - 716." type="book chapter">Gu 2002</bibRefCitation>
; Chiba 2008), this species was not included. Thus, 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1882" box="[338,459,671,695]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Halpe" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sikkima">
<emphasis box="[338,459,671,695]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">H. sikkima</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
remained a mysterious species in 
<collectingRegion box="[872,952,672,695]" country="China" name="Hainan" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">Hainan</collectingRegion>
, and its occurrence on the island needed reconfirmation. During a collecting trip at Wuzhishan (
<figureCitation box="[734,797,706,729]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="2.[151,244,1985,2007]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,226,1934]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1436,226,1934]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 3. Landscape of Wuzhishan, Hainan, China. Photographed by Guoxi Xue." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1438063/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">Fig. 3</figureCitation>
) in 2015, a male 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1882" box="[982,1096,705,729]" class="Insecta" family="Hesperiidae" genus="Halpe" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="86" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sikkima">
<emphasis box="[982,1096,705,729]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="86">H. sikkima</emphasis>
